===Noun Phrase===
'''[[power]] [[line]]'''
#A [[wire]], [[cable]] or [[conduit]], suspended in the air over [[telephone pole]]s or [[transmission tower]]s, or [[buried]] [[underground]], used for the [[carrying]] of [[electricity]] either from a power [[generating station]] to a [[substation]], or from a substation to a [[building]] such as an office or a [[home]].  Also known as a ''[[power transmission line]]''.